OL,3,CThames Water boss says he's 'angry'
OL,4,Cover water pollution
OL,6,FWater bosses could face up to two
OL,7,Fyears in prison under new government
OL,8,Fplans to crack down on water companies
OL,9,Fthat damage the environment, as ITV
OL,10,FNews Business and Economics Editor
OL,11,FJoel Hills reports
OL,13,FThe chief executive of Thames Water
OL,14,Fhas said he is angry about water
OL,15,Fpollution as new legislation comes in
OL,16,Fthat could see bosses put in prison if
OL,17,Ftheir company fails to meet certain
OL,18,Fstandards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
