OL,3,CThames Water boss says he's 'angry'
OL,4,Cover water pollution
OL,6,F"I want to clean up rivers, and that's
OL,7,Fwhy I joined Thames (Water) and now
OL,8,Fthere's a job of work to do," Chris
OL,9,FWeston told ITV News. "I understand
OL,10,Feveryone's angry - as am I."
OL,12,FThe new legislation allows regulators
OL,13,Fto bring criminal charges against
OL,14,Fexecutives from water companies, which
OL,15,Fcould lead to imprisonment.
OL,17,FAdditionally, it enables faster and
OL,18,Fmore severe fines for poor
OL,19,Fperformance, and to ban bonuses if
OL,20,Fexecutives fail to meet certain
OL,21,Fstandards.
