OL,6,FMr Weston refused to answer multiple
OL,7,Fquestions about whether he thinks he
OL,8,Fshould give up his bonus, which
OL,9,Ftotaled #195,000 for the first three
OL,10,Fmonths of this year.
OL,12,FWater bosses could face up to two
OL,13,Fyears in prison under new government
OL,14,Fplans to crack down on water companies
OL,15,Fthat damage the environment.
OL,17,FUnder previous laws, the maximum
OL,18,Fpunishment for polluting was a fine,
OL,19,Fbut new legislation put before
OL,20,FParliament on Wednesday could see
OL,21,Fwater bosses face jail time.
