OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said
OL,7,Fthat British waterways "are now in an
OL,8,Funacceptable state".
OL,10,F"Under this government, water
OL,11,Fexecutives will no longer line their
OL,12,Fown pockets whilst pumping out this
OL,13,Ffilth. If they refuse to comply, they
OL,14,Fcould end up in the dock and face
OL,15,Fprison time.
