OL,3,CThames Water boss says he's 'angry'
OL,4,Cover water pollution
OL,6,FIn a speech at Thames Rowing Club in
OL,7,FPutney, Reed said the former
OL,8,FConservative government was "too weak"
OL,9,Fto stop water companies paying out
OL,10,Fmillions in bonuses and dividends at
OL,11,Fthe expense of infrastructure upgrades.
OL,13,F"The public are sick and tired of our
OL,14,Frivers being full of filthy, toxic
OL,15,Fsewage and there being no
OL,16,Faccountability back to the sector," he
OL,17,Fadded.
