OL,6,F"The environment agency is massively
OL,7,Funder resourced. I think the funding
OL,8,Fhas been cut by around 40% in the last
OL,9,Ffew years, and that means they can't
OL,10,Fpossibly hope to keep up with all the
OL,11,Fregulation that's required," Tessa
OL,12,FWardley, director for communications
OL,13,Fand advocacy at The Rivers Trust, told
OL,14,FITV News.
OL,16,FThe quality of England's rivers, lakes
OL,17,Fand seas has plummeted in recent years
OL,18,Fas the number of sewage spills has
OL,19,Fincreased.
